column2: select    m.mangaid, m.ra as ra1, m.dec as dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra as ra2,   o.dec as dec2, s.logMass_median, s.cModelAbsMag_r--, z.nvote, z.p_el as elliptical, z.p_cw as spiralclock from MyDB.MyTable as m      cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) as n   join PhotoObj as o on n.objidd=o.objid   join stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as s on o.specObjID=s.specObjID   --join DR8.ZooSpec as z on n.objid=z.objid   --where z.nvote>=# and z.p_el>#
